	<div id="ae-intructions-panel" class="collapse shadow-sm">
		<div class="card">
			<div class="card-body ae-instructions">
				<p>This type of KML export uses the <b>current map extent</b> to limit which features are downloaded.</p>
				<b>This type of KML export may fail if:</b>
				<ul>
					<li>The request is of too many features</li>
					<li>The request covers too large an area</li>
				</ul>
				<b>Therefore if the KML download fails:</b>
				<ul>
					<li>Zoom the map closer and/or</li>
					<li>Pan the map to an area with fewer features.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
